      • equalsMethod

        com.squareup.javapoet.MethodSpec equalsMethod(TypeElement typeName,
                                              Iterable<? extends Element> elements)
        Generates an equals method over the specified elements. Only instances of typeName will be considered in the generated equality test and all of elements must evaluate to equal values.

      • hashCodeMethod

        com.squareup.javapoet.MethodSpec hashCodeMethod(Iterable<? extends Element> elements)
        Generates a hashCode method over the specified elements. Each elements evaluated value will be included in the generated hash code algorithm.

      • toStringMethod

        com.squareup.javapoet.MethodSpec toStringMethod(Iterable<? extends Element> elements)
